metadata.name: Mecha Wars
metadata.description: A futuristic world with a really revolutionary Robotic Technology which is really powerful to destroy anything in their way and an Evil organization Made to Concur this tech to rule the world so they started making Fighting Macha Robots to get that tech. For defending the tech and City An organization stabilized to counter the Mecha Attacks but there weapon were too weak to counter mecha attack so they used that tech to make a humanoid Mecha Robot to prevent the enemy attack and that Mecha was a success but enemy keep doing their attacks and a war begins between Mecha to defend the city and it turn out to be a MECHA WARS.
